cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is about face recognition using deep neural networks, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper proposes a new loss function to improve the discriminative ability of the deep features, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of margin-based methods, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV, followed by cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, and cs.NE.
